      <title>澳大利亚气候金融家敦促选民支持独立人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/australian-climate-financier-urges-voters-to-back-independents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚气候活动家和金融家西蒙·霍尔姆斯（Simon Holmes）呼吁在即将举行的选举中为独立立法者而沮丧的选民，在即将举行的选举中为独立立法者提供支持，从而在潜在的悬而未决的议会中给予了更大的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/australian-climate-financier-urges-voters-to-back-independents</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 06:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国召集沃尔玛报道了价格降价需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-summons-walmart-after-report-of-price-cut-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，在美国零售商敦促其大陆供应商吸收美国贸易关税增加之后，中国周二召集沃尔玛公司的高管表示关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-summons-walmart-after-report-of-price-cut-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾最高投资银行紧张，随着政治风险的上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/top-philippine-investment-bank-nervous-as-political-risk-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特（Rodrigo Duterte）因致命的毒品战争而​​被捕，这增加了政治风险，这可能会促使公司权衡计划以筹集资金的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/top-philippine-investment-bank-nervous-as-political-risk-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:28:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟以关税报复为目标260亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/eu-launches-metals-tariff-retaliation-on-26-billion-of-us-goods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周三针对新的美国金属关税发起了对策，并计划将自己的职责施加为260亿欧元（283亿美元）的美国商品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/eu-launches-metals-tariff-retaliation-on-26-billion-of-us-goods</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
