    <item>
      <title>特朗普的贸易战争随着金属关税激发欧盟的报复而扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-take-effect-with-no-exemptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周三生效了钢铁和铝进口的25％关税，随着全球贸易战进入一个新的风险阶段，欧盟的报复引发了报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-take-effect-with-no-exemptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 04:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
